{"tid":190524,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"比d咁ga對手巴巴托斯..is侮辱..哈","createTime":"2017-04-07T07:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T15:14:33.000Z","uid":13138,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7565d86ab5d03fdb8a405c4cbd38ba47c564895","tid":190524,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"作為一個巴巴迷 咁既終極大戰真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈鐵華團贏左有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班巴巴迷 totally no mood to 睇大結局live 嗱,我又分析下 首先黑鬼,唔好玩啦 on9仔黎，穩陣<br />\n<br />\n痴線妹,,如果係咖哩就有可觀性(順便可以報朱古力ga仇)(不過算啦,返到地球又會見到面) <br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 好似叫 乜撚野劍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我地出班細路練下is ok,又贏<br />\n<br />\n加上我地3大尖刀 三日月,昭弘,哈修 加上關鍵王尤金.. 根本場場大炒班號角,,,,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手巴巴托斯..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"444285855bc543f92dca3be340086d91563f0e2b","tid":190524,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"原來叫 破滅魔劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中二到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩具槍黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e902405f5e74407c8253460df693670cecb37e79","tid":190524,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/183149_31aa85d711872d4dd6863befa49ec325.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F183149_31aa85d711872d4dd6863befa49ec325.gif&h=35fd8bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/183149_31aa85d711872d4dd6863befa49ec325.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F183149_31aa85d711872d4dd6863befa49ec325.gif&h=35fd8bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/183149_31aa85d7